{"tid":2067110,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"搬左出黎之後重拾煮飯passion, 開心share","createTime":"2020-06-16T18:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T15:32:50.000Z","uid":335964,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df981ec106b4a56428c34d94e055af49c811a292","tid":2067110,"uid":335964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T18:21:24.000Z","msg":"利申：好多年前做過西廚幾個月<br />\n<br />\n而家香港經濟低迷，苦海求天，細佬好鍾意fine dine但又冇錢，唯有自己煮。<br />\n<br />\n去圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8ZVtLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8ZVtLV.jpg&h=0de34327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKatsu Sando AKA 吉烈和牛三文治<br />\n<br />\n專登買左塊冰鮮a5返黎炸到脆脆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ueFYrzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FueFYrzd.jpg&h=379343a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用現成tonkatsu汁，加入shallot溶，蛋黃醬，少少檸檬汁同埋法國芥末調一調再查上塊rest完嘅吉烈牛到。<br />\n<br />\n最後toast塊日本方包，查D牛油再夾住，切邊。<br />\n<br />\n一食落去D牛汁喺個口度爆曬出嚟， 雖然真係好奢侈，但係真係好食到高潮。"},{"pid":"ee30053a6aff2b702eae7f80ff184cf02fdc038a","tid":2067110,"uid":78645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T18:29:44.000Z","msg":"點解要夜晚post..."},{"pid":"02273fb05d9b310a077aac3404e208792f12fe5a","tid":2067110,"uid":335964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee30053a6aff2b702eae7f80ff184cf02fdc038a","tid":2067110,"uid":78645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T18:29:44.000Z","msg":"點解要夜晚post..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"Sorly ☺️"},{"pid":"4cfae3e0be09d4d126729007504bf15ed907e388","tid":2067110,"uid":227432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"好正<br />\n樓主可唔可以拍下片教下點煮野食?<br />\n應該會多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78c85fce6d0319b7d16fc4e990467f0c22961f1","tid":2067110,"uid":335964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cfae3e0be09d4d126729007504bf15ed907e388","